The '''Battle of Deepfires''' was a battle fought beneath [[Mount Grimmerfang]] between the [[shield dwarf|shield dwarves]] of [[Roldilar]] and the [[orcs]] of [[the Vast]] in [[north Faer没n]] in the [[649 DR|Year of the Bloody Crown, 649 DR]]. It marked the fall of the kingdom of the Roldilar.
